<author>Rosiem</author>
<title>Ka Ngai Ie Kumsawt Gam</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei suonte gitloh mawl ziekin,
 Thihna leh lungkhamna haw hi,
 Nam tin chungah a leng ui,
 Kei chunga le a tun tieng;
 Lungkham na'n ka dim sek hi.

[V2]
 Ka ngai ie kumsawt gam,
 Ka ngai ie ka Pa gam khu; Thagau in ei puiin,
 Hehpihte chawlhna mun chu, ei tun teiin.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel hinkhuo ka ngaih tuohin,
 Lunga mawlin ka lung a zing;
 Thapham muol a liem u hin,
 Bangkim ka gel kimvel tieng,
 Ka lungkhamna a khawk diek.

[V4]
 3. Hehpih chiehsate ka thilin,
 Phamsate ngaiin ka sama;
 Nung lam ngailo in leng ui,
 Lalchutphah chu kimvel in,
 &quot;Hallelujah&quot; ti'n leng ui.

[V5]
 4. Van khawpi thaka ka tuntieng
 Gibang kikhenna bei tan a
 Lungdeih cheng kimna munah
 Angel vam serafim tawh
 Lal lungnem chu awi tang kau.</lyrics>
</song>